OL,3,CManchester to fall silent as city
OL,4,Cmarks nine years since terror attack
OL,6,F22 people were killed and hundreds
OL,7,Fmore were injured when suicide bomber
OL,8,FSalman Abedi targeted crowds leaving
OL,9,Fan Ariana Grande concert on 22 May
OL,10,F2017.
OL,12,FThe Glade of Light - a permanent
OL,13,Fmemorial for those killed - will be
OL,14,Fthe focal point for personal
OL,15,Fremembrance and reflection throughout
OL,16,Fthe day.
OL,18,FThe memorial has the names of the
OL,19,Fvictims written into stone which forms
OL,20,Fa halo around a central garden near
OL,21,FManchester Cathedral.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
