OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779459070
OL,3,CManchester to fall silent as city
OL,4,Cmarks nine years since terror attack
OL,6,FFlowers will be laid at the site on
OL,7,Fbehalf of the city by the new Lord
OL,8,FMayor of Manchester Cllr Shaukat Ali,
OL,9,FCouncil Leader Bev Craig and Council
OL,10,FChief Executive Tom Stannard.
OL,12,F"Manchester will never forget those
OL,13,Fwho lost their lives in the 22 May
OL,14,F2017 terror attack, nor the many
OL,15,Fothers who were injured or otherwise
OL,16,Faffected", Bev Craig said.
OL,18,F"Time passes but we will not allow
OL,19,Ftheir memories to fade.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
