OL,3,CManchester to fall silent as city
OL,4,Cmarks nine years since terror attack
OL,6,F"On the ninth anniversary of that
OL,7,Fterrible day, we also remember the
OL,8,Fremarkable solidarity shown by the
OL,9,Fcity in refusing to give in to hatred
OL,10,F- and the resilience and courage shown
OL,11,Fby the loved ones of those who were
OL,12,Fkilled and by survivors."
